    <item>
      <title>DBS即将离任的首席执行官Gupta在“另一个横幅年”中获得了1300万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/dbs-outgoing-ceo-gupta-gets-13-million-in-another-banner-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[DBS Group Holdings Ltd.提高了首席执行官Piyush Gupta的2024年总报酬，提高了56％，理由是该银行的创纪录利润，出色的财富业务和加强技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/dbs-outgoing-ceo-gupta-gets-13-million-in-another-banner-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 00:55:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着日本的收益率激增，德国债券溃败将全球化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/japan-s-10-year-bond-yield-reaches-highest-since-june-2009</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本的政府债券收益率在十多年来达到了最高水平，澳大利亚和新西兰的收益率也飙升，因为德国巨石的溃败通过全球债务市场回荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/japan-s-10-year-bond-yield-reaches-highest-since-june-2009</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 00:27:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
