      <title>看跌赌注撤退，jd.com设定季度销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/bearish-bets-retreat-as-jd-com-set-for-jump-in-quarterly-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卖空者正在退出JD.com Inc.股票，中国在线零售商将于周四报告季度销售，这是北京消费者的贸易补贴所推动的。]]></description>
